 are retained during\nlong-term cycling, even after 2000 cycles at 50 % compression. Furthermore, the\nPTFE functionalization renders the framework structure highly hydrophobic,\nresulting in stable electrical properties, even when immersed in water for up\nto 30 days. The here presented concept overcomes the previous limitations of\nstrain-invariant soft conductors and demonstrates for the first time a\nversatile approach for the development of innovative multi-scaled and\nmulti-layered functional materials, for applications in soft electronics,\nenergy storage and conversion, sensing, catalysis, water and air purification,\nas well as biomedicine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 07:36:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-26"}
