erging diagnostic needs. Diagnostics based on this\nplatform which we term Disposable Plasmonics Assays, would be suitable for\nlow-cost screening of multiple pathogens or biomarkers in a near point of care\nsetting.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 12:25:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
