st chips was recorded with a high bandwidth oscilloscope and\nused to study the charge-sensitive amplifier of the chips in terms of waveform\nanalysis. A beam telescope was used as a reference system to allow for\ntrack-based analysis of the recorded data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Oct 2022 12:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-06"}
